        <updateDate>2023-03-07T16:27:01Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Private Student Loan Bankruptcy Fairness Act of 2023 </b></p> <p>This bill modifies the treatment of certain student loans in bankruptcy.</p> <p>Specifically, it allows&nbsp;private student loans to be discharged in bankruptcy&nbsp;regardless of whether&nbsp;a debtor&nbsp;demonstrates&nbsp;undue hardship.&nbsp;Under current law,&nbsp;student loans may be discharged in bankruptcy only if the loans impose an undue hardship on the debtor.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
